            "id": 6427576,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 華東(8110)大漲7.03%，報49.45元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華東(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8110:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8110\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8110-TW</a>)21日12:49股價上漲3.25元，報49.45元，漲幅7.03%，成交11,924張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華東(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8110:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8110\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8110-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為CC01080電子零組件製造業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌5.04%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.23%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,657 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,850 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-424 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+231 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
